        <h1 class="export-title">Chapter 5: SQL JOINs</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Combining Data from Multiple Related Tables</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 22px; color: #475569;">
            Focus: One-to-Many Relationships • LEFT JOIN • Analytical Use Cases<br>
            Example Question: "When is each fresh fruit/vegetable in season, locally?"<br>
